---

<div>
  <div class="text-center mb-12">
    <span class="eyebrow">What makes DEVS different</span>
    <h2 class="mt-5 text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white">
      Real engineering, from day one
    </h2>
    <p class="mt-4 text-lg copy-muted max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      Not theory. Not classroom busywork. Real-world skills that real teams expect.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto space-y-8 text-left">
    <div class="flex gap-5">
      <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-11 h-11 rounded-lg bg-[var(--color-accent)]/10 border border-[var(--color-accent)]/25 flex items-center justify-center">
        <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-[var(--color-accent)]" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"/></svg>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-2">Practical first</h3>
        <p class="text-sm copy-muted">Every lesson leads to working code. No filler, no theory without application.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="flex gap-5">
      <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-11 h-11 rounded-lg bg-[var(--color-accent-2)]/10 border border-[var(--color-accent-2)]/25 flex items-center justify-center">
        <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-[var(--color-accent-2)]" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 6V4m0 2a2 2 0 100 4m0-4a2 2 0 110 4m-6 8a2 2 0 100-4m0 4a2 2 0 110-4m0 4v2m0-6V4m6 6v10m6-2a2 2 0 100-4m0 4a2 2 0 110-4m0 4v2m0-6V4"/></svg>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-2">Team ready</h3>
        <p class="text-sm copy-muted">Master Git, code review, sprint flow—the tools and habits real teams use daily.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="flex gap-5">
      <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-11 h-11 rounded-lg bg-[var(--color-accent)]/10 border border-[var(--color-accent)]/25 flex items-center justify-center">
        <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-[var(--color-accent)]" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M16 7a4 4 0 11-8 0 4 4 0 018 0zM12 14a7 7 0 00-7 7h14a7 7 0 00-7-7z"/></svg>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-2">Built by a dev</h3>
        <p class="text-sm copy-muted">Created by someone who's been through the gap. We know exactly what's missing.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
